This is a SBC system capable of recommending 1-3 books from a 50-60 books to a reader from a particular reader characteristics'. 1 to 31 to 3 
It will have the greatest possible resemblance to the interaction with an expert and must give a result similar to what he would give.
The difference between this system and others used to recommend books is that our to provide a solution similar to that which would give the reader his trusted bookshelf
